# =========================================================================
# Cargo.lock - IMPORTANT NOTE
# =========================================================================
# For BINARY crates (like this command-line application), you SHOULD
# commit the `Cargo.lock` file. This ensures that anyone who builds your
# project gets the exact same dependency versions, leading to a
# reproducible build.
#
# For LIBRARY crates, you would typically add `Cargo.lock` to this file.
# We are intentionally leaving it out.
